<span data-controller="decision"><strong># Decision <%= @current_decision.id %> Results</strong>

<strong>## Question: <%= @current_decision.question %></strong>
Context: <%= @current_decision.context %>

<strong>## Results</strong>

| Approvals | Option               |
| --------- | -------------------- |
<% @current_decision.results.each do |result| %>| <%= "#{result.approved_yes || 0}".rjust(9, ' ') %> | <%= result.option_title.slice(0, 20).ljust(20, ' ') %> |</span>
<% end %>
